org.ggp.base.util.gdl.model

Class GameFlow

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ggp.base.util.gdl.model.GameFlow

  • public class GameFlow
extends java.lang.Object
    GameFlow describes the behavior of the sentences in sentence forms that depend on which turn it is, but not on the actions of the player (past or present). These include step counters and control markers.
    Author:
    Alex Landau
